entry.title: Maine Mass Shooting Suspect Found Dead
entry.content: The suspect in the worst mass shooting in the U.S. this year was found dead of an apparent self-inflicted gunshot wound Friday night, law-enforcement officials said.

entry.title: Israeli Army Expands Ground Operations as U.S. Pushes for Pause
entry.content: Israel said it was increasing ground raids and hitting Gaza with intense airstrikes, while Washington called for a temporary halt in the fighting to allow for hostage releases.
